OL,3,CArrest made over attempted bomb attack
OL,4,Con Lurgan police station
OL,6,FA 35-year-old man has been arrested in
OL,7,Fconnection with an attempted car bomb
OL,8,Fattack on Lurgan Police Station.
OL,10,FThe New IRA said they carried out the
OL,11,Fincident which saw a pizza delivery
OL,12,Fdriver hijacked in Kilwilkie and
OL,13,Fforced to drive a pipe bomb to the
OL,14,Fstation on the night of March 30.
OL,16,FThe device did not explode but was
OL,17,Fdeemed to be viable, before being made
OL,18,Fsafe and being tested for forensics.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
