PN,41902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1783700376
OL,3,CArrest made over attempted bomb attack
OL,4,Con Lurgan police station
OL,6,FA 47-year-old man has appeared in
OL,7,Fcourt charged with attempted murder
OL,8,Fand an attempt to cause an explosion
OL,9,Fin relation to the incident.
OL,11,FDetectives from the Police Service of
OL,12,FNorthern Ireland's (PSNI) Terrorism
OL,13,FInvestigation Unit announced another
OL,14,Farrest on Thursday.
OL,16,FSearches of a number of properties
OL,17,Fwere carried out in the Portadown area
OL,18,Fand items including electronic devices
OL,19,Fwere seized.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
