FL,420,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1783700376
OL,3,CArrest made over attempted bomb attack
OL,4,Con Lurgan police station
OL,6,FThe 35-year-old man was arrested under
OL,7,Fthe Terrorism Act.
OL,9,FThe PSNI said: "The attack, which put
OL,10,Finnocent lives at risk, took place on
OL,11,Fthe night of Monday March 30.
OL,13,F"The investigation is continuing, and
OL,14,Fpolice have reiterated their appeal
OL,15,Ffor anyone with information to contact
OL,16,Fthem on 101.
OL,18,F"Information can also be shared with
OL,19,Fthe independent charity Crimestoppers,
OL,20,Fwith 100% anonymity, on 0800 555 111
OL,21,For online at www.crimestoppers-uk.org."
OL,26,@qD@POUuD@AOUzD@AOU}D@gO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
