CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1783700376
OL,3,CArrest made over attempted bomb attack
OL,4,Con Lurgan police station
OL,6,FThree others were arrested in May in
OL,7,Fconnection with the incident.
OL,9,FBarry Anthony Toman, aged 47, with an
OL,10,Faddress at Drumnamoe Avenue in Lurgan,
OL,11,Fappeared before Craigavon Magistrates'
OL,12,FCourt where he was described as a
OL,13,F"committed, violent terrorist" as the
OL,14,Fcourt was told his DNA could be found
OL,15,Fon five different parts of the bomb.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@^O]
