PN,41905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1783700376
OL,3,CArrest made over attempted bomb attack
OL,4,Con Lurgan police station
OL,6,FToman was charged with attempted
OL,7,Fmurder, an attempt to cause an
OL,8,Fexplosion, and hijacking by compelling
OL,9,Fa person to drive a car carrying an
OL,10,Fimprovised explosive device relating
OL,11,Fto the attack near Lurgan PSNI station.
OL,13,FHe was also charged with possession of
OL,14,Fexplosives with intent to endanger
OL,15,Flife on a date before March 31.
OL,17,FA 39-year-old woman and a 15-year-old
OL,18,Fboy were also arrested during the
OL,19,Finvestigation.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/6
